---++ Introduction

Pigeon-tools is based on [[Trash/Trash/MonitoringInformation/RSV][RSV]] and will use RSV and apache to display results of storage tests.

Pigeon-tools is not supported in OSG 3, it is available only in OSG 1.2 and documented in Trash.ReleaseDocumentationRSVPigeonTools that explains how to use and configure pigeon tools to monitor storage elements that support a VO.

---++ *Comments*
